narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I went from knowing nothing about AML/CTF to being both informed and passionate about the subject.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Readings are always informative and interesting. The same can be said for the many notable guest speakers that are brought in. The final paper was a great opportunity for students to apply their existing knowledge and expertise to AML/CTF. Finally, being able to learn from Professor King and the other students made this class uniquely special.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I have already recommended this course to anyone who sounds remotely interested.
